{"tid":1776530,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"【暴徒停手-譴責聲明】","createTime":"2019-12-09T15:06:25.000Z","updateTime":"2019-12-09T15:10:42.000Z","uid":25558,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"ae6fc837d92151945aab34bf0aebf85684949b06","tid":1776530,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-09T15:06:25.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.nextmgz.com/article/2_712988_0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.nextmgz.com%2Farticle%2F2_712988_0&d=qnVsOlgekcepRBzFpIlw%2F5bpPLVkgxcsq72qYZiHPFQ%3D&h=e5da9eec\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.nextmgz.com%2Farticle%2F2_712988_0&h=37ddf249\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.nextmgz.com/article/2_712988_0</a><br />\n<br />\n【暴徒停手-譴責聲明】<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://vmagimg.next.hk/images/apple/20191209/1536pix/1575863956_614e.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fvmagimg.next.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple%2F20191209%2F1536pix%2F1575863956_614e.jpg&h=a000d497&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n本刊記者於12月9日早上，在黃大仙港鐵站拍攝「大三罷」行動期間，五名戴口罩男女疑是有組織而來的「藍絲」，將我們包圍並出手阻礙拍攝，當中有人企圖搶奪記者的攝錄器材，導致記者手腕受傷。<br />\n<br />\n本刊對於有暴徒針對記者行使暴力，並妨礙香港新聞自由，予以強烈譴責。本刊不容任何人以暴力干擾記者採訪，使香港蒙上暴力恐嚇陰影，也保留對暴徒的一切追究權利。<br />\n<br />\n壹週刊編輯部<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://vmagimg.next.hk/images/apple/20191209/1536pix/1575857906_12d3.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fvmagimg.next.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple%2F20191209%2F1536pix%2F1575857906_12d3.jpg&h=801fb84e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://vmagimg.next.hk/images/apple/20191209/1536pix/1575857907_17d4.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fvmagimg.next.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple%2F20191209%2F1536pix%2F1575857907_17d4.jpg&h=b165a396&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n-----------------------------<br />\n<br />\n【壹週刊直播平台 ChannelNEXT】<br />\n<br />\n全城抗暴 區區論壇同你深度剖析<br />\n<br />\n立即睇"},{"pid":"18c56f679023a0e7c7c09eaf8daf9e73ffd7ae66","tid":1776530,"uid":165683,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-09T15:06:44.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"38af29ab0fa50b61b5d1b38d99f1e90b2500b1ad","tid":1776530,"uid":259329,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-09T15:08:07.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"27022053a7df15daaed65aad25de8e08261c39ff","tid":1776530,"uid":127553,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-09T15:10:42.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/UmKV2z6.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FUmKV2z6.jpg&h=241aee25&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n有班教育界痴線佬為左唔比學生落入聖誕節圈套<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1776399\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1776399</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"}]}